I know you using shortcuts between the drivers This could much a different Till now its just you that repost this We used rclone union over rclone rc command Between mergerfs + rclone union is this a big difference

Mergerfs ( local ) + rclone union ( remote ) = 2 layer // remote + download s = unionfs
Without mergerfs: Rclone union ( remote + local ) = 1 layer // remote + download s = unionfs
